<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965218>
    dc:description "FIGURE 49. Genitalia of Siberian Sterrhinae. A, B—Timandra recompta; C, D—T. paralias; E, F—Lythria purpuraria; G— Rhodostrophia vibicaria; H—R. jacularia; I—Idaea serpentata; J—I. dohlmanni. A, D, E—genital segment; B, C, F—phallos; G–J—bursa copulatrix of female. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965218/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965232>
